This is a pack of unix utilities for handling some administrative tasks. Now in development and in alpha-status. 
Available commands:

mysqlbackup - simple tool for backup mysql data
mysqlrestore - restore databases from backups
siteadd - add virtual host to Apache config and create new database in mysql
dbadd - create new database and database user
dbuseradd - create only new database user
changelog - tool for watch changes made by other utilities (incompleted).

Planned tools:
* integration with backup-manager
* control of maradns
* create virtual hosts for Nginx

More information on http://dradm.org and http://dradm.ru (documentation now only in Russian).
Author contact: Alexander I.Grafov <axel@dradm.org>
